加高車身及加大車體內部以容納通訊器材和地圖桌，車頭外部加裝小型發電機 <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.warwheels.net/SaracenCommandpostINDEX.html |title=warwheels.net-FV 610 (A) |access-date=2008-04-04 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122030000/http://warwheels.net/SaracenCommandpostINDEX.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
